        "created_at": "2018-06-25T13:43:23.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"William Kelley\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n William Kelley:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Notice much botrytis influence? The 2013 Chevalier is very marked by botrytis, but I haven\u2019t tried the '13 Les Chaum\u00e9es.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Didn\u2019t really notice any botrytis.  Wine is full but perfectly balanced.  The acidity ensures the wine is neither cloying nor goopy.</p>",
